Brice Boxing Promotions will be streaming the “ Battle of the Young Guns “ tournament on 30 August 2019 live from the Wynberg Military Base in Cape Town. JOHANNESBURG - Brice Boxing Promotions will be streaming the “ Battle of the Young Guns “ tournament on Friday night live from the Wynberg Military Base in Cape Town. The event offers an exciting lineup of young Cape Town boxers, including the warrior Jimmy "Wrong Turn" Mabundji in action as well as the destructive force that is SA Heavyweight star Tian Fick. Making his pro debut is former Western Cape and CTMOBO champion Farhaaz Sayed. Boxing is scheduled to go live at 7pm and you are invited to watch the fights by logging onto the following link: www.streamit360.tv/#873-1258.